ChelGbtqEeg0O34WgzBQA">Nhạc Châu thành thượng - 岳州城上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-N%C3%A3i/author-Fd7oZerPVEVOXx_JIj1fmg">Diêu Nãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-32k659mWc_gB4dFFUMtrsw">Sơn cư tức sự - 山居即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%E1%BB%A9c-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Ti%E1%BB%83u-uy%E1%BB%83n-th%C3%AD-xu%C3%A2n-y/poem-mw0WX0k6V8PxDqhD4p0n1g">Tức nhật (Tiểu uyển thí xuân y) - 即日（小苑試春衣）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-yWTSGr8hXuUY0oV4ZjMvoQ">Xuân nhật tức sự - 春日即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br></div>	</div>
